dct_title_s: Schetskaart van de Schouten- en Padeaido Eilanden
dct_description_sm: J. M. Baretta ; Feuilletau de Bruijn.
Relief shown by shading and spot heights.
Inset showing "Mios Pondi or Mios Korwar" (Bepondi) Island.
Shows low water, vegetation, small islands, towns, horse and foot paths, marsh/swamps, etc.
